title: 1996, Q3 Flood Data, BLACK HAWK, IA
name: 1996, Q3 Flood Data, BLACK HAWK, IA
description:
The Q3 Flood Data are derived from the Flood Insurance Rate Maps (FIRMS) published by the Federal Emergency Management Agency (FEMA).   The specifications for the
horizontal control of Q3 Flood Data files are consistent with those required for mapping at a scale of 1:24000.
